{"tid":1447281,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"關於不合作運動VS民意，我有嘢講","createTime":"2019-08-11T15:44:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T23:34:50.000Z","uid":203845,"like":36,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"ba81f9399b417ff15dd407c167cb6506bafb58d1","tid":1447281,"uid":203845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:44:51.000Z","msg":"社會運動可以分成兩種，一種係短期，一種係長期<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">短期嘅通常係指革命，政變等</span><br />\n<br />\n特色係用武力，激進嘅手法進行。但係唔需要依賴市民支持（有當然更好），唔會有好多持續性。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">喺呢種情況下，武力會成為運動成功同失敗嘅關鍵。</span> <br />\n因為係用武力逼對方妥協嘅手段<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">長期嘅通常係指非直接達成目的嘅運動, 包括遊行，集會，甚至長期佔領</span><br />\n<br />\n特色係用較溫和嘅手法進行，但係同時對民眾影響大，需要大量人民配合，而且要佢地持續支持<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">喺呢種情況下，民意會成為關鍵。因為係靠大量民意向政府施壓</span> <br />\n同時唔同嘅長期抗爭手段，都係要市民配合<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n即係點？<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">即係如果你地班人唔係諗住直接革命，民意都係重要！<br />\n<br />\n不合作運動冇可能即時令政府妥協，你長做就變咗擾民，而唔係對準政權，到時就玩完</span><br />\n<br />\n我明大家今日好嬲，但係大家都要冷靜諗下，點樣先可以做得更好<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n建議：<br />\n1. 勇武暫時退一退，今日好需要賽後檢討<br />\n2. 民宣重煲721同今日警黑，動搖政府管治威信<br />\n3. 和理非應該盡快搞大遊行，再做多次百萬人示威<br />\n4. Be smart。所有人一定要諗清楚，要思考，唔好咁易比人帶風向<br />\n而家我地已經比人嚴重滲透<br />\n連登係，前線都係。所以請用腦"},{"pid":"78f4cc250aaafef5a7cc6fa6d57afe9d44adc071","tid":1447281,"uid":4645,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:44:59.000Z","msg":"全面不合作運動 癱瘓香港<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1445565\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1445565</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"d67f6cb5e210abdb1d032900aa37afa07c0de6ad","tid":1447281,"uid":203845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"78f4cc250aaafef5a7cc6fa6d57afe9d44adc071","tid":1447281,"uid":4645,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:44:59.000Z","msg":"全面不合作運動 癱瘓香港<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1445565\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1445565</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:45:50.000Z","msg":"花少少時間睇咗先<br />\n而家不合作真係唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a79592d1038089a25ccbcbdb5ade91805b120bf8","tid":1447281,"uid":203845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:46:43.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e2a3db339720665cab6bf07d9d92169ac335915","tid":1447281,"uid":301692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:46:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"844254cd143d1444cf2c5ce7e3f9f7dd08127e2d","tid":1447281,"uid":203845,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:47:32.000Z","msg":"想搞不合作運動嘅唔該睇睇<br />\n唔係唔可以不合作，但係要有目的<br />\n同正當性"},{"pid":"f180853adfbe20e3e08b56897915bc3b305a404e","tid":1447281,"uid":203845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:48:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2980aeba1cfe718c55b25a98ddeebdbe85121d39","tid":1447281,"uid":203845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:49:02.000Z","msg":"自推十次"},{"pid":"ab1693fba6fad2e44e95626d08f4a6ad4a49b44d","tid":1447281,"uid":54303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:50:43.000Z","msg":"心水清！"},{"pid":"f9df680eb729ee319234b0bfd6fadcd656a6eb69","tid":1447281,"uid":203845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:50:49.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"3bb13940ac559b2d7f391a26cc2fbec9ebedcd9d","tid":1447281,"uid":203845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ab1693fba6fad2e44e95626d08f4a6ad4a49b44d","tid":1447281,"uid":54303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:50:43.000Z","msg":"心水清！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:51:59.000Z","msg":"要推比其他人睇<br />\n太多人圍爐<br />\n我地一開頭都係靠民意<br />\n100萬人升級，然後勇武"},{"pid":"1db3c3c182de45456712464169eba7681d93fb78","tid":1447281,"uid":203845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":